  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Wick Whittlestick</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafwick.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafwick.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Wick Whittlestick</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Steward\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Steward\">steward</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wick_Whittlestick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wick_Whittlestick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wick is stationed at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wick_Whittlestick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Wick guards the ice cells and opens the door to <a href=\"/index.php/Cregan_Karstark\" title=\"Cregan Karstark\">Cregan Karstark</a>'s cell when Lord Commander <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> arrives to interrogate the prisoner.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Wick is among the members of the Night's Watch who become dissatisfied with how Lord Commander Snow is leading them. He is the first of the conspirators to attack the Lord Commander after Jon announces his intentions to lead an army of <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a> to attack <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Ramsay Bolton</a>. Wick slashes at Jon's neck with a knife, grazing him, but is eventually disarmed by Jon. As explanation for his actions, he states that it is \"for the Watch\" while the other conspirators begin their attack in the <a href=\"/index.php/Mutiny_at_Castle_Black\" title=\"Mutiny at Castle Black\">mutiny at Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wick_Whittlestick&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafwick.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafwick.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Wick.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd49.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_49\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 49\">Chapter 49</a>, Jon X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd69.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_69\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 69\">Chapter 69</a>, Jon XIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404073248\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.072 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.257 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 657/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10568/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6455/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 504/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2198/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.49 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  246.232      1 -total\n 97.15%  239.217      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.34%  237.215      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.56%   28.468     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.51%    8.653      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.49%    8.586      5 Template:Ref\n  2.07%    5.085      5 Template:Ref/core\n  0.97%    2.379      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    0.952      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in pars